{"tid":1724032,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中大理大- 諸神黃昏Ragnarok","createTime":"2019-11-15T10:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T11:34:36.000Z","uid":171788,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0a56fb9fb0c76b13619ba3eedd75a20cb321fdf2","tid":1724032,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:58:37.000Z","msg":"中大 理大 手足 <br />\n請你地棄守學院<br />\n<br />\n你哋校長提早完sem 係想你地有放棄陣地嘅勇氣<br />\n真正嘅中大理大 係入面D人 唔係建築物 <br />\n唔好攬住死物唔放<br />\n<br />\n離開左學院 仲可以偏地開花 <br />\n死守只會被圍剿<br />\n而家我哋係露出一個好大嘅目標比人肅清 <br />\n<br />\n我哋面對嘅人 係卑鄙同更卑鄙嘅人<br />\n唔好為呢啲事送頭<br />\n<br />\n請你明白校長嘅用意<br />\n大學已經保護唔到你 <br />\n呢個係校長最後可以為學生做"},{"pid":"b461bb6db9e7d50aef1e60276e5fc11f691274e5","tid":1724032,"uid":139671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"但係中大建築物都重要"},{"pid":"adc9beed4161081506e389291c3511ae5725f249","tid":1724032,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"22009f1c7d6a85d2d0ce43550845af16e8b46338","tid":1724032,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:14:33.000Z","msg":"你攻 好過去守啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1e19cab2c635cac92baef499552b668b082b08","tid":1724032,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/grFe3sA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgrFe3sA.jpg&h=370674cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大 理大 火種要相傳落去更重要"}]}